elements.viewExpression: CASE #ahvp WHEN 10 THEN "aucune" WHEN 20 THEN "basse" WHEN 30 THEN "normale" WHEN 40 THEN "élevée" WHEN 50 THEN "urgente" WHEN 60 THEN "immédiate" END

CASE #aivj WHEN 10 THEN "8-Fonctionnalité" WHEN 20 THEN "7-Simple" WHEN 30 THEN "6-Texte" WHEN 40 THEN "5-Cosmétique" WHEN 50 THEN "4-Mineur" WHEN 60 THEN "3-Majeur" WHEN 70 THEN "2-Critique" WHEN 80 THEN "1-Bloquant" END

CASE #akau WHEN 10 THEN "1-Nouveau" WHEN 50 THEN "2-Affecté" WHEN 20 THEN "3-Commentaire" WHEN 52 THEN "4-Soumis communautaire" WHEN 55 THEN "5-Corrigé" WHEN 60 THEN "6-Appliqué test" WHEN 65 THEN "7-Appliqué prod" WHEN 70 THEN "10-Proposition commerciale" WHEN 80 THEN "8-Résolu" WHEN 90 THEN "9-Fermé" END

CASE #alar WHEN 10 THEN "Ouvert" WHEN 20 THEN "Corrigé" WHEN 30 THEN "Rouvert" WHEN 40 THEN "Impossible à reproduire" WHEN 50 THEN "Impossible à corriger" WHEN 60 THEN "Doublon" WHEN 70 THEN "Pas un bug" WHEN 80 THEN "Suspendu" WHEN 90 THEN "Ne sera pas corrigé" END
CASE WHEN #adbw IN('_smeynieux','_ccroullebois','_fsomers','_asuzuki','_vgrousset','_lducos') THEN 'Pôle support' WHEN #adbw LIKE '\_%' THEN 'BibLibre hors support' ELSE 'Hors BibLibre' END
CASE WHEN #adnb IN('_smeynieux','_ccroullebois','_fsomers','_asuzuki','_vgrousset','_lducos') THEN 'Pôle support' WHEN #adnb LIKE '\_%' THEN 'BibLibre hors support' ELSE 'Hors BibLibre' END
